{"tid":2392799,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【倫敦】侍應、售貨員有力置業","createTime":"2021-02-03T04:35:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T05:07:36.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"52e4b38d371bdc7e649aa74dafdf5765e0af2e98","tid":2392799,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T04:35:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210203/STMPNLKSBVEXBNVZE5AKRYUDFQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210203%2FSTMPNLKSBVEXBNVZE5AKRYUDFQ%2F&d=FM8PVMPbIH5fyb1BVmxPrUt47LdDf8L2Tg6pYSR3Psk%3D&h=8af4bfd0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210203%2FSTMPNLKSBVEXBNVZE5AKRYUDFQ%2F&h=445eba91\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210203/STMPNLKSBVEXBNVZE5AKRYUDFQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n【倫敦】侍應、售貨員有力置業<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/QJ-7fmM5wBHtmI8KMDrK09mTKGM=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/L4WAFJGLMVAVJC5WZQC63ABABQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FQJ-7fmM5wBHtmI8KMDrK09mTKGM%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FL4WAFJGLMVAVJC5WZQC63ABABQ.jpg&h=72ab374e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■藝術家Cody表示，倫敦與香港有很多相似的地方。<br />\n<br />\n倫敦為英國最繁榮城市，不負首都之名。在倫敦住逾20年、從事藝術的蔡嘉樂（Cody）形容，倫敦在國內「最有活力」，資訊、科技等領先全國，若有心在事業拼搏，適合在此落腳，尤其從事藝術與金融業。不過他亦認同，自居家令以來，越來越多人遷出倫敦。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【卡迪夫】空氣水質佳 物價較低<br />\n<br />\n「倫敦係最似香港嘅城市。」Cody形容，自己是「要住喺城市嘅人」，在香港很喜歡旺角那種熱鬧，倫敦在這方面最似香港，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第四區低於300萬<br />\n<br />\n粗略概括，合租屋（Shared-house）第一區月租達800英鎊（約港幣8,500元）或以上，第二區則為600至700鎊（約港幣6,400至7,400元），第三、四區則約。。。。。。。。。。，「做人最緊要有啲目標可以追到。」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【利鎮】樓價低至70萬有交易<br />\n<br />\n多年來Cody在第一至四區都住過，強調治安難單以第一至四區劃分，。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n居於倫敦市中心的不少是單身、力爭上游的人，。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/KShB8stblenbWyqnPxobXzaRiig=/887x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GBDSNLGQFNAJJCM2PU5VZJ2OF4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FKShB8stblenbWyqnPxobXzaRiig%3D%2F887x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGBDSNLGQFNAJJCM2PU5VZJ2OF4.jpg&h=20daefba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■Cody認為倫敦是個重視藝術的地方，從事此行業者可在這裏浸養靈氣。"},{"pid":"9c38c64c6345f68edad32c824b7e1ab2839f8c82","tid":2392799,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T05:04:30.000Z","msg":"月租HKD8500<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1547f5e37eabf241145e28568d2235e867fe7930","tid":2392799,"uid":221490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T05:07:36.000Z","msg":"我紐西蘭個朋友話 當地人兩夫婦做侍應都可以置業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}